    <string name="exploit_waiting_msg">Waiting for app-vulnerable to trigger Vector 4 (FileProvider).</string>
    <string name="how_it_happened_desc">app-vulnerable\'s FileProvider is configured with &lt;root-path path=\"/\"> in res/xml/file_paths_vulnerable.xml. This maps the FileProvider root to the device\'s root directory, allowing any content:// URI to reference any file the victim app can access — including its own SharedPreferences.\n\nThe victim app sent this app a FLAG_GRANT_READ_URI_PERMISSION Intent, delegating read access for the specific URI. ContentResolver then opened the file on our behalf via the victim\'s FileProvider process.</string>
